  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Content & Marketing Strategist",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Plan, develop and Develop and implement a content strategy aligned with business objectives for the Company and our Clients.</li>\n  <li>Conduct market research and competitor analysis to identify opportunities.</li>\n  <li>Gather potential leads through marketing campaigns and input into CRM system for sales team to follow up on.</li>\n  <li>Develop and execute integrated marketing campaigns across various channels, including email, social media, and SEO/SEM.</li>\n  <li>Oversee pre planning, on-set production and post-production editing processes.</li>\n  <li>Manage content calendar and ensure timely delivery of high-quality content for all projects.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with design and video production team to produce engaging visual content on social media.</li>\n  <li>Create high-quality content, including blog posts, social media posts, case studies, articles etc</li>\n  <li>Develop social media strategies and content for the Company and its projects.</li>\n  <li>Track and analyze marketing performance metrics to measure ROI and optimize strategies.</li>\n  <li>Set up paid and organic social media campaigns.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with creative team to create visually appealing and engaging content.</li>\n  <li>Responsible for full project management and scheduling for social media marketing projects.</li>\n  <li>Maintain brand consistency across all marketing materials and channels.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Marketing, Communications or relevant field of study.</li>\n  <li>3+ years of experience in content marketing, advertising and/or digital marketing.</li>\n  <li>Passion for marketing and loves to express ideas visually</li>\n  <li>Strong understanding of SEO, SEM, social media marketing, and email marketing.</li>\n  <li>Ability to manage multiple projects simultaneously and meet deadlines.</li>\n  <li>Ability to create simple graphics (aesthetic FB/IG stories) and an eye for design.</li>\n  <li>Strong attention to detail and organizational skills.</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work independently in a fast-paced setting with strong project and time-management skills</li>\n</ul>",
